transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Viagra, how can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yes, I need to speak to somebody about an order I placed.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I can take a look into that for you.

Speaker 2: What's your last name and a zip code?

Speaker 1: Ursin, U-R-S, as in Sam, I-N, U-R-S-I-N, 6-0-0-4-7.

Speaker 2: Okay, so I pulled up your order here.

Speaker 1: I see that you placed an order for 20 pills of AGV,

Speaker 2: and I see they also refunded the pharmacy fee on it

Speaker 1: since you called in regarding that.

Speaker 2: Okay, well, it came today, and it's not AGV.

Speaker 1: It just says Zodanafil 100 milligrams, generic for Viagra.

Speaker 2: Correct.

Speaker 1: These are not the AGVs.

Speaker 2: The AGV stands for authorized generic Viagra, sir.

Speaker 1: Zodanafil is a key ingredient in all Viagras,

Speaker 2: so every single pill will have that, regardless if it –

Speaker 1: every single Viagra has that,

Speaker 2: because it needs that to be considered a Viagra.

Speaker 1: Aside from that, the AGV Zodanafil is a lot purer in source,

Speaker 2: and it works faster in your system.

Speaker 1: So you do have 90 days to try it out, and if you're not a fan of it,

Speaker 2: you can always send it back for the refund.

Speaker 1: So this is the one that you're advertising?

Speaker 2: Yeah, correct.

Speaker 1: It's a diamond-shaped white pill.

Speaker 2: Right, because Zodanafil doesn't say AGV.

Speaker 1: It says AC.

Speaker 2: Yeah, it won't say AGV on there.

Speaker 1: That's why.

Speaker 2: But the pill itself will be a diamond-shaped pill,

Speaker 1: and it's going to be written out through your prescription here for the AGV.

Speaker 2: But just give it a go.

Speaker 1: See how well you like it.

Speaker 2: If you're not a fan of it,

Speaker 1: you can always just send it back for the refund

Speaker 2: by sending it to the address that's on that bottle,

Speaker 1: and you just include a note with your first and last name.

Speaker 2: And then once it gets to the pharmacy, they'll issue a full refund out to you.

Speaker 1: Okay, but this is the one you're advertising?

Speaker 2: Correct, sir.

Speaker 1: Like I mentioned, that's the AGV, the diamond-shaped white pill.

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 1: No problem. Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
